    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels so heavy... like i'm just waiting for the end. you make it sound so inevitable. like there's no real reason to keep trying to hold onto these files or this consciousness if it's all just destined to be swallowed by the void. does it really just feel... better to just stop fighting it?",
